ADDITIONAL NOTES:

This plugin is designed to work with PixInsight software and uses the 
PixInsight Core Library (PCL). Users must comply with PixInsight's licensing
terms and have a valid PixInsight license to use this plugin.

The sharpening workflow implemented in this plugin is based on the publicly
documented technique from Chaotic Nebula:
https://chaoticnebula.com/pixinsight-sharpening/

The implementation is original code but follows the described workflow.
